title: Proposal for a Scream.sh Partnered Stake Pool and Farm
body:
**SpookySwap Welcomes Scream.sh to Partnered Staking!**
xBOO holders, today we are happy to be able to offer you the first partnered staking pool featuring SCREAM, a DeFi lending protocol that facilitates the borrowing of crypto assets by using real world and DeFi assets as collateral.

**The xBOO Pool:**
Stake xBOO tokens to earn SCREAM tokens!
* Total Tokens: 1700 SCREAM
* Distribution duration: 60 days
* Start time: 1630328400 August 30th, 2021 1300 UTC
* Finish time: 1635512400 October 29th, 2021 1300 UTC
* Token rewards per second:  0.0003279 SCREAM

**The Farm:**
In addition to the SCREAM xBOO Pool, we would provide a SCREAM-FTM farm that will have 0.8x BOO rewards for the first 48 hours and then 0.4x BOO rewards after that.

**What is SCREAM Finance?**
SCREAM is a decentralized lending protocol built on the Fantom network. SCREAM leverages the highly-scalable and high-throughput capabilities of Fantom to provide cheap lending and borrowing solutions for mass adoption. SCREAM aims to build high-velocity markets for more traditional crypto-asset lending services, but with the goal of improving overall capital-efficiency across a wider range of Fantom-based assets.  

**To learn more about SCREAM Finance, grim advises you to visit their official communication channels:**
* Website: https://scream.sh
* Twitter: https://twitter.com/screamdotsh
* Telegram: https://t.me/screamsh
* Discord: https://discord.com/invite/BBu3599TnH
* Blog: https://screamsh.medium.com/

**How do you stake xBOO to earn SCREAM rewards?**
If you own BOO tokens, congratulations! You’re one step away from staking xBOO. It’s easy to learn how to stake xBOO for Partnered Staking.
* Visit this webpage: https://spookyswap.finance/pools
* Click “Approve” on the Buyback BOO Single Stake pool
* Click on the “+ Stake” button
* Enter your amount of BOO
* Confirm the transaction, this will get you xBOO
* Then, click “Approve” on the SCREAM Pool
* Click on the “+ Stake” button
* Enter your amount of xBOO
* Confirm the transaction
